Alice.name: Alice
Alice.description: young girl, long blond hair tied back, wearing a Victorian dress

mad.description: young girl, mad expression on her face, long blond hair tied back, wearing a Victorian dress

Neck-Stretching Alice.description: young girl, with comically long neck, elongated neck, long blond hair tied back, wearing a Victorian dress

Mad Hatter.name: Mad Hatter
Mad Hatter.description: A quirky, eccentric character with wild, orange hair. He wears a large top hat with a card marked '10/6' and is often seen at the tea party.

Queen of Hearts.name: Queen of Hearts
Queen of Hearts.description: A tyrannical and quick-tempered queen, dressed in a red gown with heart motifs, and often depicted with a small golden crown.

White Rabbit.name: White Rabbit
White Rabbit.description: A nervous, fussy character, always in a hurry, and often seen with a pocket watch.

Cheshire Cat.name: Cheshire Cat
Cheshire Cat.description: A mischievous, grinning cat, often depicted with a wide, toothy smile and bright, glowing eyes.

Caterpillar.name: Caterpillar
Caterpillar.description: A wise, philosophical character, often depicted sitting on a mushroom and smoking a hookah.

Tweedledee and Tweedledum.name: Tweedledee and Tweedledum
Tweedledee and Tweedledum.description: A pair of rotund, identical twins, often depicted wearing matching outfits and engaging in nonsensical conversations.

March Hare.name: March Hare
March Hare.description: A quirky, eccentric character with wild, orange hair. He wears a large top hat with a card marked '10/6' and is often seen at the tea party.

Dormouse.name: Dormouse
Dormouse.description: A sleepy, timid character, often depicted dozing off or hiding in a teapot.
